Di luar akan turun hujan.

274
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,300
Kemana kamu pergi, Nona?

275
00:12:04,930 --> 00:12:06,460
Mungkinkah penginapan sederhana saya terlalu kumuh

276
00:12:06,460 --> 00:12:08,120
